      "text": [
        "2269 - وَمَنْ مَاتَ فِي طَرِيقِ مَكَّةَ ذَاهِبًا أَوْ جَائِيًا أَمِنَ مِنَ الْفَزَعِ الْأَكْبَرِ يَوْمَ الْقِيَامَةِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2269 - Whoever dies on the way to or from Makkah will be safe from the Great Terror on the Day of Judgment."
        ]
      }
    }
